data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: This image shows two adult women at a bar. A short-haired woman in a white shirt turned her back to us, and another long-haired woman faced us in a red and white dress. The image also shows several glasses of beer on the table at the bar, next to a woman's green bag. This picture gives us a very quiet and relaxed atmosphere. This reminds me of a time I once went to a bistro with a friend. We really enjoyed this relaxed and pleasant atmosphere, and at the same time we could make a lot of like-minded friends. This image left a lasting impression on me and brought back fond memories of the past.（115）
